Title: Himalaya Under Eye Cream(15 ml)
Description: Eyes are the primary indicators of your age, so it is very important for us to take proper care of the dark circles. With the Himalaya Under Eye Cream, you can naturally treat your beautiful eyes and get them glowing. The effective Under Eye cream from Himalaya contains proven and safe blend of herbs that are specially created to care for the delicate area around your eyes. This prevents further formation of under eye dark circles and also reduces the existing ones. The dark circles appear because of the comparatively thinner layer of skin around the eyes, which is not endowed with oil glands as the rest of the body. Subsequently, as we age, the skin becomes dry and wrinkled thereby showing signs of aging. The dark circles are formed as the veins in the lower eye area appear more prominently. The Himalaya Under Eye cream is ideal for women as it helps them reduce the dark circles thereby condensing its nutritional deficiency. This cream will help you diminish pigmentation and blemishes found underneath your eyes. Adding on, the Under Eye Cream from Himalaya also brightens and soothes the dark areas under your eye.  The cream contents like cipadessa baccifera, Triticum vulgare moisturize the skin and the presence of Bergenia ligulata helps in lightening the skin under your eyes. The Triticum vulgare also adds a nourishing touch to your beautiful skin thereby adding a touch of glamour to your face. Directions to Use: Gently massage the delicate area under your eyes after thorough cleansing. Use the Himalaya Under Eye Cream twice a day on a regular basis to get spotless skin in about four weeks.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Body and Skin Care>Eye Care>Eye Creams
